use npm to install flow-bin:
ubuntu@ubuntu:~/git_root/react2/react-boilerplate-app$ npm install --save-dev flow-bin  
  
Add this line into package.json:
  "scripts": {
    ...
    "flow": "flow"
  },

  npm run flow init

  npm run flow

  If all these are fine, add this line into ~/.bashrc

  alias flow='npm run flow'
  

  Add this line to the beginning of the file:
  // @flow

  install flow-for-vscode extension